summary: An ordinance amending Section 1 of Ordinance No. 8860 entitled: "An ordinance licensing and regulating theatres, concrete halls, and other public amusements of like character in the City of Seattle, and providing a penalty for violation thereof and repealing Ordinance No. 7729, approved February 7, 1902, and Ordinance No. 8030, approved April 28, 1902", approved November 18, 1902.
